<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "db568a8e862aa2d714f1f6f1a47488d8505bceaa40fa3022fd63a36caa0152af" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 3.3 兼容性\n\n- 目标产物栈：Web 全栈 JavaScript/TypeScript（前端 React/Next.js 类，后端 Node.js/Serverless 类，关系型数据库）。\n- [ASSUMPTION] 代码生成目标在 v1 仅支持 TypeScript 单语言、模块化单仓；多语言支持为后续项。\n- 执行引擎接入：优先 ACP 中立协议（Claude Code / Codex 经 adapter 接入），回退 Agent SDK 或无头 CLI（F-018）。\n- Web 原型预览：现代主流浏览器（Chrome/Firefox/Edge 最新稳定版）；移动端浏览器不在 MVP 范围。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
