<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-013%3A%20%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%B6%E5%85%89%E6%9C%BA> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/contains_entity> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/AC-005> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-013%3A%20%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%B6%E5%85%89%E6%9C%BA> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "F-013: 意图日志与时光机" .
