<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-013%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/contains_entity> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-013> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-013%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "F-013: 开发者交接包" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-013%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "F-013: 开发者交接包" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "8874e0597de3e7230d395a52335eb4af516111d40177b56a99ffe9247cc9e7ab" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### F-009: 改动影响预览（Blast Radius）\n\n- **用户故事**: 作为用户，在我提出需求之前，我希望看到这次改动会影响哪些功能区块，以便我有把握做决定，不会误伤其他部分。\n- **验收标准**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: 基于蓝图依赖图，在地图上高亮本次变更将触及的能力节点与模块边界（blast radius）。\n  - [ ] AC-002: 影响预告以通俗语言表达：「会碰这 N 个区块：[区块名列表]，不会碰 [安全区块名列表]」。\n  - [ ] AC-003: 预览所示影响范围与实际改动范围一致，无明显漏标（漏标率为 0）。\n  - [ ] AC-004: 影响预告在蓝图 diff 确认界面中同步展示，不需要额外操作。\n  - [ ] AC-005: 开发者版支持 PR 图级 diff 与 blast radius 高亮，集成在 CI 检查中。\n- **优先级**: P1\n- **备注**: blast radius 计算依赖蓝图依赖图的完整性；依赖图有环或信息缺失时降级展示（[ASSUMPTION]）。\n\n---" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
