<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "2a4e78725d7fa1efae289acf4735fb2abddc5f5f680e6d9e6d8ef64a11a3a106" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 4.3 关键假设\n\n- **核心假设 R1**（须优先安排最小验证）：蓝图能否同时做到机器可检与非程序员可读。这是产品成立的前提。\n- [ASSUMPTION] 自动修复代理层（消费门禁结构化错误静默自愈）的自愈策略与上浮判定逻辑待架构阶段设计，本 PRD 只声明功能意图（F-005）。\n- [ASSUMPTION] LLM 编排的按依赖 DAG 拓扑序调度，精准上下文注入，具体调度协议待架构阶段确定。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "4.3 关键假设" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "4.3 关键假设" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.3%20%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "4.3 关键假设" .
