<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "7125b1a185abf3ce2d17358d8b2023c5cf1ed6eeb1b8674b650eed3f98e4b951" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 4.4 调研记录\n\n- 产品统一决策：`ADR-0011`（聚焦非程序员单一产品，开发者工具产品线移出范围）\n- Web 原型先行决策：`ADR-0002`（先用现有三张 Web 原型测试核心假设，嵌入式为后续项）\n- 参考技术报告：「形式化输入 → 确定性变换规则 → 可验证输出」三元式（见 `archive/meta-model.md` §1）" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "4.4 调研记录" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "4.4 调研记录" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.4%20%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "4.4 调研记录" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-015%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-015%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "706b46283848d7108bc0e018545277ffcb30a2151049055de69a1b3d74e4d975" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-015%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### F-015: 开放代码与一键导出\n\n- **用户故事**: 作为用户，我希望随时能把我的应用代码完整带走，且在没有 Keel 的情况下，代码仍能被开发者继续维护。\n- **验收标准**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: 随时可触发导出：生成结构服从蓝图的标准 JS/TS 仓库。\n  - [ ] AC-002: 导出物含编译落地的标准工具配置（dependency-cruiser / eslint / tsconfig / JSON Schema），脱离 Keel 运行时后，这些标准工具仍能独立强制执行结构约束。\n  - [ ] AC-003: 导出物为可独立运行的标准项目；未参与 Keel 的开发者可直接用标准工具（npm / node / git）继续开发。\n  - [ ] AC-004: 导出物不包含 Keel 专有运行时依赖；不包含凭据或内部服务地址硬编码。\n  - [ ] AC-005: 导出完成提示中说明「此项目已包含架构约束工具配置，脱离 Keel 亦可自我强制」。\n- **优先级**: P1\n- **备注**: 「脱离 Keel 的独立强制」的验收方式：导出后在无 Keel 环境下运行 eslint / dependency-cruiser，结构违规应被检出（[ASSUMPTION]）。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-015%3A%20%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
