<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20B%20%C2%B7%20%E6%96%B0%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20B%20%C2%B7%20%E6%96%B0%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "313b2d3a51fbc7b0e68e5f2053e1b6eeedb4eaea2cb5d25e85e4bf2db38c73d7" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20B%20%C2%B7%20%E6%96%B0%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 流程 B · 新项目上手\n\n1. 新建项目，检测执行引擎；缺失则图形化安装引导，经应用登录完成鉴权，全程无终端命令。\n2. 描述应用意图或选起步模板，自动选定 `modular-monolith` 架构原型。\n3. 生成初始蓝图与可运行骨架，能力地图首次渲染。\n4. 引导用户加第一个能力，进入流程 A。" .
