<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "c838df4eb41843c74c94d7b0da1f251726a83bb077c722162fb7dd9aa5b3f79e" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 流程 D · 导出与交接\n\n1. 用户在项目设置选择导出代码或生成交接包。\n2. 导出标准 JS/TS 仓库（含编译落地的标准工具配置 dependency-cruiser / eslint / tsconfig / schema），脱离 Keel 仍能自我强制结构。\n3. 生成开发者交接包：蓝图转架构文档、意图日志转决策史、边界规则转上手指南。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
