<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "4acaa5ec3402f023215246c12835ffbd9dcfa3006fa9185e8ac39162f4b1bd52" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 流程 D · 一键上线\n\n1. 用户点击上线，系统运行安全体检：认证配置 / 数据权限 / 密钥泄露三类红绿灯检查，输出安全分。\n2. 存在红灯时阻断上线，逐项给出通俗说明与修复入口（可触发流程 C）。\n3. 全绿后部署到锁定技术栈的托管环境，向用户返回可访问地址。\n4. 上线动作记入意图日志，时间线可回滚。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "流程 D · 一键上线" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20D%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "流程 D · 一键上线" .
