<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-007%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-007%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "7e7637906f354f9e9e5ad0a0ff0124f115659847fc93e2ac13d6703a1bd12221" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-007%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### F-007: 改动影响预览（Blast Radius）\n\n- **用户故事**: 作为用户，在我提出需求之前，我希望看到这次改动会影响哪些功能区块，以便我有把握做决定，不会误伤其他部分。\n- **验收标准**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: 基于蓝图依赖图，在地图上高亮本次变更将触及的能力节点与模块边界（blast radius）。\n  - [ ] AC-002: 影响预告以通俗语言表达：「会碰这 N 个区块：[区块名列表]，不会碰 [安全区块名列表]」。\n  - [ ] AC-003: 预览所示影响范围与实际改动范围一致，无明显漏标（漏标率为 0）。\n  - [ ] AC-004: 影响预告在蓝图 diff 确认界面中同步展示，不需要额外操作。\n- **优先级**: P1\n- **备注**: blast radius 计算依赖蓝图依赖图的完整性；依赖图有环或信息缺失时降级展示（[ASSUMPTION]）。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-007%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-007%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "F-007: 改动影响预览（Blast Radius）" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-007%3A%20%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88%EF%BC%88Blast%20Radius%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd> .
