<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20C%20%C2%B7%20%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E8%B0%83%E5%92%8C> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20C%20%C2%B7%20%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E8%B0%83%E5%92%8C> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "452088382605edd33c2f00bc21edc5c4855609687931b21d58d10ac3e1460257" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20C%20%C2%B7%20%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E8%B0%83%E5%92%8C> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 流程 C · 健康预警与调和\n\n1. 健康灯转黄或红，问题清单出现通俗描述的具体项（如「收藏功能被实现了两遍，建议合并」）。\n2. 用户点选某项，显示通俗说明与修复入口。\n3. 触发调和：以受影响切片的冻结契约为锚，驱动引擎整片重生成该切片（非就地修补），受门禁约束。\n4. 修复后回归校验通过，健康灯恢复，记入意图日志。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20C%20%C2%B7%20%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E8%B0%83%E5%92%8C> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
