<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-013> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> ": 意图日志与时光机" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-013> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_section> "F-013: 意图日志与时光机" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "0e50c19e8ddb9ddd4c0ebe27a22af14fb4efb3d693fd76a6429ef50ebfc8b621" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 流程 A · 主循环：加一个能力\n\n1. 用户在对话面板用通俗语言描述需求；也可先选中地图节点再描述（指图说话，F-009）。\n2. 系统产出蓝图 diff，在地图上以高亮与差异标注呈现，并给通俗解释与受影响能力清单（「会碰这 N 个区块，不会碰…」）。\n3. 用户确认、追加修改（回到第 2 步）、或拒绝。\n4. 确认后先冻结本次涉及的接口契约与数据 schema，再驱动引擎针对冻结契约逐切片实现；每次编辑经过门禁，硬违规即拦截并自动重试，软问题记录健康。\n5. 进度以能力地图节点状态变化展示（规划中 → 实现中 → 已就绪），不向用户暴露代码或终端输出。\n6. 实现完成后运行回归守护与漂移检测，健康灯更新，记入意图日志。\n\n**异常分支**：门禁反复硬阻断且无法自动推进时，升级为「需你决策」卡片，用通俗语言说明冲突点并给出选项（F-010）。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "流程 A · 主循环：加一个能力" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "流程 A · 主循环：加一个能力" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%20A%20%C2%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "流程 A · 主循环：加一个能力" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "7f0285428e2b6fe3d1f5770dee669c7efd2e62206f106e635574792beabd2eb3" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 4.2 技术约束\n\n- **唯一真相源**：`docs/blueprint.example.yaml` 是规范蓝图实例（符合 `docs/blueprint.schema.json`）；`demo/blueprint.yaml` 已弃用（`ADR-0007`）。\n- **界面内容来源**：界面只渲染 `plain_*` 字段，技术字段一律不上界面；界面内容改动须核对 100% 来自蓝图、未从代码逆推。\n- **v1 单一架构原型**：v1 只上 1 个默认原型 `modular-monolith`（特性切片/模块化单体），由意图自动选中（`ADR-0003`）。\n- **行为门远期纳入**：当前门禁只保证结构不腐化、契约一致；行为门（契约派生单测/属性测试）为 R1 之后的远期项，现在只做 `oracle` 字段占位预留（`ADR-0009`）。\n- **门禁严重度分层**：结构性违规（破依赖边界、重复实现、契约不符）为硬阻断；风格类问题（命名、目录、轻微冗余）为软告警（`ADR-0004`）。\n- **蓝图文件格式**：探索阶段使用 YAML + JSON Schema；不上 CUE/Pkl，等到编译强制时再评估（`ADR-0010`）。\n- **需求层（R-IR）**：蓝图含 `requirements[]` 原语，带 `id / plain / acceptance[]`（含 oracle 标注）；`Unit` 与 `Constraint` 通过 `satisfies` 回链实现需求覆盖率校验（`ADR-0008`）。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "4.2 技术约束" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "4.2 技术约束" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/4.2%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "4.2 技术约束" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-014%3A%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-014%3A%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "f3d567aaa0467ed08a9f9785676708a670bc92067625fd45770825347ddd5117" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-014%3A%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### F-014: 一键上线与安全体检\n\n- **用户故事**: 作为非程序员，我希望点一下就能把应用发布给别人用，并确信系统已替我检查过安全问题，以便我不因不懂安全配置而把有漏洞的应用放到公网上。\n- **验收标准**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: 提供一键上线入口：触发后自动构建并部署到锁定技术栈的托管环境，完成后返回可访问地址；全程不出现终端命令或部署配置。\n  - [ ] AC-002: 上线门禁（安全体检）：部署前自动检查认证配置、数据权限、密钥泄露三类安全项，以红绿灯逐项呈现并输出安全分。\n  - [ ] AC-003: 存在红灯项时阻断上线，逐项给出通俗说明与修复入口；全绿后才执行部署。\n  - [ ] AC-004: 上线动作记入意图日志（F-013），时间线支持回滚到上线前状态。\n- **优先级**: P1\n- **备注**: 三类安全项的具体检查清单待安全规范阶段补充（[ASSUMPTION]）。托管环境为锁定技术栈的一部分（主卷 §4.1）；自建部署基础设施不在范围内。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-014%3A%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
